Requirements for Device Automation Libraries
--------------------------------------------

	1. Point $AUTOMOD to 'automation_apptest_script' directory
		Example:
			# Do not put anything before these lines
			export GIT_HOME=${HOME}/automation_pda
			export AUTOMOD=${GIT_HOME}/automation_apptest_script

	2. Source $AUTOMOD/rc.sh
		Example: 
		. $AUTOMOD/rc.sh

	NOTE: Make sure to put 1 and 2 in the end of the .bashrc file.
	
	Example:
		vi .bashrc

		>>> Add these lines at the top of the file and save it.
		 
		 #----
		export GIT_HOME=${HOME}/automation_pda
		export AUTOMOD=${GIT_HOME}/automation_apptest_script
		. $AUTOMOD/rc.sh
		 #-----

